        "class": "",
        "text": " - ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "As for man, his days are as grass.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Here is a new departure. From the loving kindness and mercy of God the psalmist passes to the weakness and helplessness of man. Man is like grass (",
        "children": []
